# HLCRF variant "H" -- only the Header slot renders. h.ctml appends content
# to all five slots so this tape proves NewLayout's own documented
# behaviour: a slot letter absent from the variant string is silently
# skipped even though nodes were appended to it (docs/architecture.md
# "Variant String"). NotText on the other four slots' distinct content is
# the only way to prove a slot did NOT render -- there is no Expect NotBox.

Source h.ctml
Set Width 80

Expect Text "Header slot content"
Expect NotText "Left slot content"
Expect NotText "Content slot content"
Expect NotText "Right slot content"
Expect NotText "Footer slot content"

Expect Box H
Expect Fits
